text: Colobothea assimilis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1902.BioLib.cz - Colobothea assimilis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1902
